videoSnippet.title: Soon to be Married Couple Play a Blitz Game to Decide the Family Name
videoSnippet.description:
#agadmator Melanie: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=N1P5t8uoBtI
Nikolas: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3ko_4chM6oI

Nikolas Lube vs Melanie Ohme
"Battle for the Family Name"

1. Nf3 Nf6 2. g3 g6 3. Bg2 Bg7 4. O-O O-O 5. d3 d6 6. e4 c6 7. Re1 Qc7 8. c3 b5 9. Nbd2 Nbd7 10. d4 e5 11. Qc2 Re8 12. a4 Bb7 13. axb5 cxb5 14. d5 a5 15. Bf1 Qb6 16. h3 Ba6 17. Kg2 Rec8 18. Ra1 Rb7 35. Qe3 Bf8 36. h4 Kg7 37. g5 h5 38. f4 exf4 39. Qxf4 Be7 40. Rf1 Bd8 41. Rdf3 Bb6 42. e5 dxe5 43. Qxe5+
